title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:

1. Add a table to the report which includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data.
